SQL Tuning Tools

-- Automated tools
   ADDM
   SQL Tuning Advisor
   SQL Access Advisor
   SQL Performance Analyzer
   Optimizer Statistics Advisor
   SQL plan management
   SPM Evolve Advisor
   
Note - The above tools may not always capture the culprit, sometime we need to manually investigate to identify root cuase.

-- Manual SQL Tuning Tools
   Performance views
   Display execution plans
   Tracing tools
   Optimizer hints
   
-- User Interface to SQL Tuning Tools
   SQLPlus
   Enterprise Manager Database Express
   Enterprise Manager Cloud control
   SQL developer
   
